item.title: CVE-2023-20859|2023-03-23T00:00:00 -- n%2Fa -- spring%20vault%2C%20spring%20cloud%20vault%2C%20spring%20cloud%20config
item.description: In Spring Vault, versions 3.0.x prior to 3.0.2 and versions 2.3.x prior to 2.3.3 and older versions, an application is vulnerable to insertion of sensitive information into a log file when it attempts to revoke a Vault batch token.
